com.example.suberduberuber.ViewModels

Class DriverPaidRateViewModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • androidx.lifecycle.ViewModel
      • androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
        • com.example.suberduberuber.ViewModels.DriverPaidRateViewModel

  • public class DriverPaidRateViewModel
extends androidx.lifecycle.AndroidViewModel
    This is a viewmodel class to handle the payment and ratings for the driver side of the app. It stores the driver and rider in the current request to keep them accessible throughout each of the fragments. The main functionalities of this viewmodel are to update the rider's rating and complete the request process.
